description: This Chainlink VRF common Parvati purrs with a rating of 49, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 98, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, Stringalong for East, Box for South, and Box for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/40492-57442-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [98 Votes, Common]
